Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:40.02,Title,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.8\3c&H060605&\pos(640,150)}第18话  over-cry -强袭-
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——Text——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.88,0:00:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,「双角会」的人!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,至少现在不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,只是…也不是无法理解他们的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那些不得不依赖土御门夜光的…软弱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.04,0:00:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,今春引发灵灾恐怖事件的六人部千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.26,0:00:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,还有新宿支局的咒搜部战斗的牧原义隆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.28,0:00:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我和他们是同期进入阴阳厅的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.54,0:00:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一整晚抵足长谈夜光的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.93,0:00:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,江藤先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.33,0:00:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我的这番话让你感到有些为难
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我还是想让你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人 还是对你寄托着希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.12,0:00:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是饯别老友吧 能否请你向这个东西注入些许咒力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 打扰你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:00:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,江藤先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是留他一条活命更好些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,都是伶路的错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,根本就不让我放开手脚玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,于是 这个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目 此地不宜久留
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,咦!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,春…春虎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,急急如律令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(640,660)}Order
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎大人 貌似这个瘴气也会钻入地下的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,再这样下去的话灵脉会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,「等级3」 不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(550,660)}Phase3
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,显现吧 北斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:03:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,趁现在赶紧去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,仓桥同学 叫出你的护法式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,白樱 黑枫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,看清!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙的身体 是水的集合体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,地之土 得泷火之力 将邪水拦堵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,急急如律令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(640,660)}Order
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,二位快退开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,围护我等之身 阻住潜行者的脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,急急如律令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(640,660)}Order
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 这连拖时间都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要玩也得是先跟我玩才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快变成灵灾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,北斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 这可真是棒极了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 这该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那边那几个塾生 快点走开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,第11 12小队去修禊灵灾 然后净化这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你想去哪里啊 一起来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,总之先和冬儿他们会合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,北斗进不来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,急急如律令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(640,660)}Order
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,天马
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,冬儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,仅仅这样还是有点无聊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧给我「堕落」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,压扁他!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,区区一个式神别小看人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,铃鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真是得救了 谢谢你们各位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你高兴个啥啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,已经没救了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你们全部 全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我的!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,急急如律令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(640,660)}Order
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才那一发挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,再多给我几发嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这该死的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是龙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这把刀叫做「髭切」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:15.26,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32}髭切，又名鬼切，源满仲名刀之一，后来刀传到源赖光手里，他将其中的「髭切」交给渡边纲。\N传说渡边纲用髭切在五条渡口切下鬼神茨木童子的手腕，因此髭切有了「鬼切」的称呼。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 为什么要把龙收起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,放出来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,龙 龙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,龙 放出来啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,情况不妙 开溜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,京子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,京子 你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,京子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来做诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙离开以后你就去和冬儿他们会合 听好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目 再强化一下这个结界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是春虎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,土御门同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,灵灾还没有修禊好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,到底会怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 赶紧藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那条龙 要是逼得你濒临死亡的话你会放出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,用它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,什么嘛 你没有「形代」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,要是切掉你的手或者腿 你会愿意把龙放出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你很碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,呆虎 你给我冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,把龙放出来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,放出来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦 就知道畏畏缩缩的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才装作男生欺骗周围的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个狡猾的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,耍赖 骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:57.40,Comment,,0,0,0,,给我说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不够 完全不够
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:02.11,Comment,,0,0,0,,说话啊 说话啊 耍赖 说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:05.78,Comment,,0,0,0,,你倒是吭气啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,保护夏目的灵力 咒力 甚至连灵视的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(848,660)}见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都不够
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我没法痛揍那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来就没有灵视
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(772,660)}见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我是通过这个观察到外界的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这是连接内外的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是夏目赋予我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,将精神集中到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,齿轮没有咬合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,马力和齿轮不配对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎! 春虎!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,急急如律令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(640,660)}Order
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我的原创招式!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,春…春虎君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,能行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我能干翻这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,给我住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙也能看到一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,对了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然他出现过好几次灵滞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(840,660)}Lag
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但唯有那把刀没出过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那把刀…是这家伙的「形代」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:13:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,空
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,放!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,火气 火气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要更强的灵气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我受够了 我要宰了你!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧你浑身都是破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,看招看招看招
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,强大的火气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,能和雪佛对抗的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,强力的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目 我们把他引到中庭去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要折断那把钝刀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:14:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,空
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:14:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,东海之神 名阿明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,西海之神 名祝良
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,南海之神 名巨乘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,北海之神 名愚强
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,四海之神 斥退百鬼 拔除凶灾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,急急如律令
