Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 刚才那招是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,后面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,空 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙是木气的灵灾 不好意思借我用一用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:15:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,火势比预想要大…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下去要…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,火气控制
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,火的咒术
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,偏偏是那家伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,曩莫萨缚怛他孽帝毗药
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(640,660)}归命一切如来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,萨缚目契毗药 萨缚他
