Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(595,660)}暴恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(760,660)}大忿怒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,欠 佉呬佉呬 萨缚尾觐南
